    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎加入官方玩家Q群：979926278</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《忍者明》是一款以“瞬移”为核心机制的2D平台游戏。扮演忍者“明”踏上试炼之路，飞跃8个章节、241个关卡，使用空间忍术帅气闯关。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>基本功——闪现，瞬移！</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234330/extras/a64b11fafa3a2058cd49d7e2e2918d88.poster.avif?t=1766022901\" width=620 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234330/extras/a64b11fafa3a2058cd49d7e2e2918d88.webm?t=1766022901\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234330/extras/a64b11fafa3a2058cd49d7e2e2918d88.mp4?t=1766022901\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >掷出苦无，瞬间闪现到它的位置！忍者「明」的移动全靠瞬移，掌握之后，你将化身空中飞人，体验真正的“来无影去无踪”！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234330/extras/d789edf75a71aff8ccbd722e02876d25.poster.avif?t=1766022901\" width=620 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234330/extras/d789edf75a71aff8ccbd722e02876d25.webm?t=1766022901\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234330/extras/d789edf75a71aff8ccbd722e02876d25.mp4?t=1766022901\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>习得花式忍术，破解多样地形</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「飞闪瞬移」只是入门级操作！随着关卡深入，你将解锁更多炫酷技能：用「瞬闪」实现超远距离位移，用「火球」「石壁」破坏（或建造）地形，甚至利用「替身闪」巧妙逃课！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个地形都有独特的谜题——传人符、传弹符、消波块、火龙卷……用你的技能组合制定最佳路线，拉满操作！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234330/extras/0325f51c211f98df3f918c92838bcec3.poster.avif?t=1766022901\" width=620 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234330/extras/0325f51c211f98df3f918c92838bcec3.webm?t=1766022901\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234330/extras/0325f51c211f98df3f918c92838bcec3.mp4?t=1766022901\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索解谜，收集忍者卷轴</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通关之余也别忘了探索——每个关卡都带有收集物「卷轴」！简单直接的「普通卷轴」、需要多次飞闪解锁的「闪现卷轴」、用钥匙开启的「宝箱卷轴」、悬空挑战的「计时卷轴」，以及藏在角落的「隐藏卷轴」。更有高难度支线房间等你挑战！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>忍者「明」的成长</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >三年前，由于时空裂隙的出现，天灾降临，忍者镜和四忍肩负守护的使命，协力封印裂隙，此后下落不明。三年后，名为「明」的忍者继承忍者意志，踏上试炼历程，重走前人路，追寻镜的下落，并完成自身的蜕变。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏内不包含数值成长，只有操作熟练度在变强，从而获得真正的成长，最终达致糅合精准、速度、优雅的忍者之风。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234330/extras/ef53a86b0486717e039b5838bae6b59e.avif?t=1766022901\" width=620 height=268 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>更多游戏特色：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>帮助模式，以慢制快</strong>：局内可自由调整游戏速度，最低可至0.3倍速</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>秘闻板块</strong>：记录忍者旅途中的见闻和习得的忍术</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>速通模式</strong>：通关任意章节即可开启。速通模式下会对通关时长进行计时，欢迎速通玩家前来挑战（目前第一章「林」世界记录102.73s，保持者Tichat002）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>丝滑操控</strong>：移动身法与技能控制都精准到位</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>瞬间复活</strong>：快速衔接，闪瞬间即可重新挑战</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>8大区域</strong>：成为忍者大师的终极试炼</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>动感的电子音乐</strong>（由4 Channels Club制作）：伴你帅气通关</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>卷轴室传送门</strong>：通关前4章节即可解锁，进入后4章节的里世界</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>神秘成就预警，大量彩蛋预警！</strong></p></li></ul>",
